VR Product Solution

















Tablet Solution

















Bluetooth Audio Solution

















WiFi Audio Solution



































S900




Actions’ S900 is a high performance low power 28nm Application Processor which integrates 64-bit Quad-Core Cortex-A53 that fully complies with ARMv8-A architecture. The advanced GPU (Graphic Processing Unit) PowerVR G6230 maximize the 3D/2D display performance and processing effect.· 28nm low power· PowerVR G6230 GPU 

                                    Read more


















ATS2829




 • ATS2829 is a single-chip highly integrated Bluetooth Audio solution. Satisfies the market requirements with higher performance, lower cost and power consumption, which is designed for portable and wireless audio products. · Bluetooth headset function, supporting BT V4.2 dual mode· full format audio playback, build-in stereo audio codec, SNR>98dB· motion detector for step，distance and calories calculation· heart rate detector· support external temperature and humidity sensors· data upload to smart phones through Bluetooth via SPP /BLE· Support Android system APK control and IOS system APP control· Actions own intellectual property algorithm SV2.X for echo cancelation and noise repression

                                    Read more




































































