                        2016




ATM705X and ATS2805 received title of “Hi-Tech Product”
Named a “High-tech Enterprise”
VR Chip Solution Received the Most Promising Product Award in the 11th Chinese Chip Award Ceremony
Named “Actions (Zhuhai) Technology Center”
Named “Zhuhai Multimedia Communication IC Engineering Technology Center”
Received National Patent Award for “A Method and Device To Reduce CPU Consumption During Vector Graphics Filling”
Received Patent Award for “A Battery Charge Method and Device” in Guangdong Province
Received title of “National IP Enterprise”
Received title of “Provincial IP Enterprise” in Guangdong





                        2015




Received title of “Municipal IP Enterprise” in Zhuhai 
Received Patent Award for “A Method and Device To Reduce CPU Consumption During Vector Graphics Filling” in Guangdong Province
Received Patent Awards for “An IC with Scan Chain Technique” and “A USB Device and its Test Method”









                        2014




Named 2014 China Outstanding IC Design Enterprise
32-bit SoC Chipset received Outstanding Product Reward at the 16th Annual China
                        High-Tech Conference
“Actions” and “炬力” received Guangdong Provincial Trademark Certificate
“Key Technology & Application of Low Power Multimedia Series Chipset” Project received
                        2nd Place Guangdong Technology Improvement Award.
Received the High Growth IC Design Enterprise Award
Quad-core Android tablet SoC the ATM7029 received the China Semiconductor Innovative
                        Product and Technology Award at the 8th Annual IC Market China Conference





                        2013




“Quad-core tablet chipset ATM7029” received the Most Promising Product Award in
                        the 8th Chinese Chip Award Ceremony
Recognized as a Key High-Tech Enterprise in the National Torch Plan
