                        Guangdong Outstanding Patent Award
“Android tablet SoC solutions ATM7019 and ATM7013” received the 2012 China Semiconductor
                        Innovative Product and Technology Award at the IC Market China 2013
Named a Key IC Design Enterprise of 2011-2012 National Strategic Plan





