Actions Semiconductor Co., Ltd. Revenue and Financial Data

   Portable media players are the bread and butter of this firm. Actions Semiconductor is one of China's leading fabless semiconductor companies. Competition and the global recession, which slowed sales of consumer electronics, have dampened Actions' sales. The company designs system-on-a-chip (SoC) products for the development and manufacture of battery-powered, portable consumer electronic devices that capture, store, and play digital media files, such as compressed audio, image, and video files, including MP3 players. Five value-added distributors in China collectively account for nearly two-thirds of the company's sales. Customers located in China and Hong Kong provide nearly all of sales.
  







